Part 2 of ?

My parents have been worried a lot recently, they try not to show it, but I can see it.

The weekly performance at the theatre always cheers them up though, and they say that as soon as I have my next birthday I can join them! I can almost smell it now, with the vendors bringing freshly baked bread down the aisles, and the mead flowing free...
